## 2026-05-12

The following changes are reflected in the MICA-7t v3.0

### Rename `desc-` to `rec-` in anatomical filenames

Replaced the `desc-` string with `rec-` in all anatomical filenames across subjects and sessions to comply with BIDS naming conventions.

```bash
for i in sub*/ses*/anat/*desc-*; do mv -v $i ${i/desc-/rec-}; done
```

---

### Add `acq-07mm` string to unlabelled MP2RAGE, UNIT1, and T1map files

For files in `ses-a*` sessions that match `MP2RAGE`, `UNIT1`, or `T1map` and do not already carry an `acq-05mm` or `acq-cstfl` string, insert `acq-07mm_` right after the session string in the filename.

```bash
for file in $(find sub*/ses*/anat/ \( -name "*MP2RAGE*" -o -name "*UNIT1*" -o -name "*T1map*" \) ! -name "*acq-05mm*" ! -name "*acq-cstfl*"); do
    ses=$(echo "$file" | grep -oP 'ses-a[^_/]+' | head -n 1)
    mv -v "$file" "${file/${ses}_/${ses}_acq-07mm_}"
done
```